，上一代完成唔到嘅嘢，就會留畀下一代，我都希望係咁，有啲嘢，如果我達成唔到，我希望我嘅觀眾可以達成到。」他說自己才剛起步，不知道可以走得多遠，但正如他在雜誌的專欄欄目，「半世功名一芥輕」，人生最重要是活着的狀態。<br />\n「達哥；2013年；人中之龍5 夢之繼承者」"},{"pid":"8162194e5a9e0f662876d16d8eefde0a259ccd02","tid":1781953,"uid":13782,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T14:45:02.000Z","msg":"又想洗白<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bffebb8f00af93d84174c0c79142d8a19e3a9cc3","tid":1781953,"uid":81644,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T14:45:50.000Z","msg":"憑直播打機上位的達哥林慧韡，近年有多線發展，又拍廣告又拍電影，2014 年更成為手機遊戲公司副總裁，做出名氣。奧柏中國（8148）投資 800 萬元搞手機遊戲，找來達哥開設手機遊戲公司「達魂製作」（Touch Fun Productions）出任公司 CEO，冀招兵買緊，尋找本地人才，一同製作出本地原創手機遊戲，預計 2018 年第 4 季推出。<br />\n<br />\n出未,好想玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d51f3911ac7a971d9200eeac8c27ef256c706ce","tid":1781953,"uid":79562,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0f3ba12828bbeced4a176d7fe20bc09dc5be41c6","tid":1781953,"uid":19334,"like":1,"dislike":11,"score":-10,"quote":{"pid":"afb759eb6c6f6fd0460684c4324b9760fce2030d","tid":1781953,"uid":339272,"like":24,"dislike":1,"score":23,"quote":{"pid":"e7d1f1d054528f68ce06561e87bacff6555ce7cd","tid":1781953,"uid":208402,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T14:20:27.000Z","msg":"各自爬山  佢真係去左爬山"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T14:31:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢爬人民幣山"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T14:34:44.000Z","msg":"你都睇左十年啦，應該都知達哥為人，係兄弟既真係在心中。其實咁耐以黎佢講過出口既，對世界各種既事既態度，你會明佢係咩立場，你講得出呢句野真係麻煩你重睇啦。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T14:49:59.000Z","msg":"出賣backup佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bb732d5ee197ba1e0a77ee345cbfcf676fd084e","tid":1781953,"uid":19334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ee918f63c1be